[
  {
    "bookname": "Micah",
    "chapter": "3",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">I <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">said</st>,<p class=\"poetry\">\u201c<st data-num=\"08085 04994\">Listen</st>, you <st data-num=\"07218\" class=\"\">leaders</st><n id=\"1\" /> of <st data-num=\"03290\" class=\"\">Jacob</st>,<p class=\"poetry\">you <st data-num=\"07101\" class=\"\">rulers</st> of the <st data-num=\"01004\" class=\"\">nation</st><n id=\"2\" /> of <st data-num=\"03478\" class=\"\">Israel</st>!<p class=\"poetry\">You <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">ought</st> to <st data-num=\"03045\" class=\"\">know</st> <st data-num=\"04941\" class=\"\">what is just</st>,<n id=\"3\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "1"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Micah",
    "chapter": "3",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">yet you<n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"08130\" class=\"\">hate</st> <st data-num=\"02896\" class=\"\">what is good</st><n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">and <st data-num=\"0157\" class=\"\">love</st> <st data-num=\"07451\" class=\"\">what is evil</st>.<n id=\"3\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">You <st data-num=\"01497 05921\">flay</st> my people\u2019s <st data-num=\"05785\" class=\"\">skin</st><n id=\"4\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">and rip the <st data-num=\"07607\" class=\"\">flesh</st> <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">from</st> their <st data-num=\"06106\" class=\"\">bones</st>.<n id=\"5\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "2"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Micah",
    "chapter": "3",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"0834\" class=\"\">You</st><n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"0398\" class=\"\">devour</st> my <st data-num=\"05971\" class=\"\">people\u2019s</st> <st data-num=\"07607\" class=\"\">flesh</st>,<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"05921 06584\">strip off</st> their <st data-num=\"05785\" class=\"\">skin</st>,<p class=\"poetry\">and <st data-num=\"06476\" class=\"\">crush</st> their <st data-num=\"06106\" class=\"\">bones</st>.<p class=\"poetry\">You <st data-num=\"06566\" class=\"\">chop</st> them <st data-num=\"06566\" class=\"\">up</st> like <st data-num=\"07607\" class=\"\">flesh</st> in a <st data-num=\"05518\" class=\"\">pot</st><n id=\"2\" />\u2014<p class=\"poetry\">like <st data-num=\"01320\" class=\"\">meat</st> <st data-num=\"08432\" class=\"\">in</st> a <st data-num=\"07037\" class=\"\">kettle</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "3"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Micah",
    "chapter": "3",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"0227\" class=\"\">Someday</st> these sinful leaders<n id=\"1\" /> will <st data-num=\"02199\" class=\"\">cry</st> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">to</st> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> <st data-num=\"02199\" class=\"\">for help</st>,<p class=\"poetry\">but he will <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">not</st> <st data-num=\"06030\" class=\"\">answer</st> them.<p class=\"poetry\">He will <st data-num=\"05641\" class=\"\">hide</st> his <st data-num=\"06440\" class=\"\">face</st> from <st data-num=\"01992\" class=\"\">them</st> at <st data-num=\"01931\" class=\"\">that</st> <st data-num=\"06256\" class=\"\">time</st>,<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"0834\" class=\"\">because</st> they have <st data-num=\"07489\" class=\"\">done</st> such <st data-num=\"07489\" class=\"\">wicked</st> <st data-num=\"04611\" class=\"\">deeds</st>.\u201d </p>",
    "verse": "4"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Micah",
    "chapter": "3",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\"><st data-num=\"03541\" class=\"\">This is what</st> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> has <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">said</st> <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">about</st> the <st data-num=\"05030\" class=\"\">prophets</st> who <st data-num=\"08582\" class=\"\">mislead</st> my <st data-num=\"05971\" class=\"\">people</st>,<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">\u201cIf someone gives them enough to <st data-num=\"05391 08127\">eat</st>,<p class=\"poetry\">they <st data-num=\"07121\" class=\"\">offer an oracle</st> of <st data-num=\"07965\" class=\"\">peace</st>.<n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">But if <st data-num=\"0834\" class=\"\">someone</st> does <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">not</st> <st data-num=\"05414\" class=\"\">give</st> them <st data-num=\"05921 06310\">food</st>,<p class=\"poetry\">they are ready to <st data-num=\"06942\" class=\"\">declare</st> <st data-num=\"04421\" class=\"\">war</st> <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">on</st> him.<n id=\"3\" /></p>",
    "verse": "5"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Micah",
    "chapter": "3",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03651\" class=\"\">Therefore</st> <st data-num=\"03915\" class=\"\">night</st> will fall, and you will receive no <st data-num=\"02377\" class=\"\">visions</st>;<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">it will <st data-num=\"02821\" class=\"\">grow dark</st>, and you will no longer be able to <st data-num=\"07080\" class=\"\">read the omens</st>.<n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">The <st data-num=\"08121\" class=\"\">sun</st> will <st data-num=\"0935\" class=\"\">set</st> <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">on</st> these <st data-num=\"05030\" class=\"\">prophets</st>,<p class=\"poetry\">and the <st data-num=\"03117\" class=\"\">daylight</st> will <st data-num=\"06937\" class=\"\">turn to darkness</st> <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">over</st> their heads.<n id=\"3\" /></p>",
    "verse": "6"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Micah",
    "chapter": "3",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">The <st data-num=\"02374\" class=\"\">prophets</st><n id=\"1\" /> will <st data-num=\"0954\" class=\"\">be ashamed</st>;<p class=\"poetry\">the <st data-num=\"07080\" class=\"\">omen readers</st> will <st data-num=\"02659\" class=\"\">be humiliated</st>.<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">All</st> of them will <st data-num=\"05844 05921\">cover</st> their <st data-num=\"08222\" class=\"\">mouths</st>,<n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">for</st> they will receive <st data-num=\"0369\" class=\"\">no</st> <st data-num=\"0430\" class=\"\">divine</st> <st data-num=\"04617\" class=\"\">oracles</st>.\u201d<n id=\"3\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "7"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Micah",
    "chapter": "3",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetrybreak\"><st data-num=\"0199\" class=\"\">But</st> <st data-num=\"0595\" class=\"\">I</st><n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"04390\" class=\"\">am full</st> of the <st data-num=\"03581\" class=\"\">courage</st> <st data-num=\"0854\" class=\"\">that</st> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>\u2019s <st data-num=\"07307\" class=\"\">Spirit</st> gives<p class=\"poetry\">and have a <st data-num=\"01369\" class=\"\">strong</st> commitment to <st data-num=\"04941\" class=\"\">justice</st>.<n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">This enables me to <st data-num=\"05046\" class=\"\">confront</st> <st data-num=\"03290\" class=\"\">Jacob</st> with its <st data-num=\"06588\" class=\"\">rebellion</st><p class=\"poetry\">and <st data-num=\"03478\" class=\"\">Israel</st> with its <st data-num=\"02403\" class=\"\">sin</st>.<n id=\"3\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "8"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Micah",
    "chapter": "3",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"08085 04994\">Listen</st> to <st data-num=\"02063\" class=\"\">this</st>, you <st data-num=\"07218\" class=\"\">leaders</st> of the <st data-num=\"01004\" class=\"\">family</st><n id=\"1\" /> of <st data-num=\"03290\" class=\"\">Jacob</st>,<p class=\"poetry\">you <st data-num=\"07101\" class=\"\">rulers</st> of the <st data-num=\"01004\" class=\"\">nation</st><n id=\"2\" /> of <st data-num=\"03478\" class=\"\">Israel</st>!<p class=\"poetry\">You<n id=\"3\" /> <st data-num=\"08581\" class=\"\">hate</st> <st data-num=\"04941\" class=\"\">justice</st><p class=\"poetry\">and <st data-num=\"06140\" class=\"\">pervert</st> <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">all</st> <st data-num=\"03477\" class=\"\">that is right</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "9"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Micah",
    "chapter": "3",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">You<n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"01129\" class=\"\">build</st> <st data-num=\"06726\" class=\"\">Zion</st> through <st data-num=\"01818\" class=\"\">bloody crimes</st>,<n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03389\" class=\"\">Jerusalem</st><n id=\"3\" /> through <st data-num=\"05766\" class=\"\">unjust violence</st>.</p>",
    "verse": "10"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Micah",
    "chapter": "3",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">Her<n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"07218\" class=\"\">leaders</st> take <st data-num=\"07810\" class=\"\">bribes</st> when they <st data-num=\"08199\" class=\"\">decide legal cases</st>,<n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">her <st data-num=\"03548\" class=\"\">priests</st> <st data-num=\"03384\" class=\"\">proclaim rulings</st> for <st data-num=\"04242\" class=\"\">profit</st>,<p class=\"poetry\">and her <st data-num=\"05030\" class=\"\">prophets</st> <st data-num=\"07080\" class=\"\">read omens</st> for <st data-num=\"03701\" class=\"\">pay</st>.<p class=\"poetry\">Yet they claim to <st data-num=\"05921 08172\">trust</st><n id=\"3\" /> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> and <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">say</st>,<p class=\"poetry\">\u201cThe <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">is</st> <st data-num=\"07130\" class=\"\">among</st> us.<n id=\"4\" /> <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"07451\" class=\"\">Disaster</st> will <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">not</st> <st data-num=\"0935 05921\">overtake</st><n id=\"5\" /> us!\u201d</p>",
    "verse": "11"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Micah",
    "chapter": "3",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03651\" class=\"\">Therefore</st>, <st data-num=\"01558\" class=\"\">because of</st> you,<n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"06726\" class=\"\">Zion</st> will be <st data-num=\"02790\" class=\"\">plowed up</st> like<n id=\"2\" /> a <st data-num=\"07704\" class=\"\">field</st>,<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03389\" class=\"\">Jerusalem</st> will <st data-num=\"01961\" class=\"\">become</st> a <st data-num=\"05856\" class=\"\">heap of ruins</st>,<p class=\"poetry\">and the <st data-num=\"01004\" class=\"\">Temple</st> <st data-num=\"02022\" class=\"\">Mount</st><n id=\"3\" /> will become a <st data-num=\"01116\" class=\"\">hill</st> overgrown with <st data-num=\"03293\" class=\"\">brush</st>!<n id=\"4\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "12"
  }
]